cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "coxstream: Exact out-of-core Cox proportional hazards regression via streaming Newton-Raphson"
abstract: >-
  coxstream fits the Cox proportional hazards model on datasets larger than RAM.
  It computes the exact Efron partial-likelihood estimate by streaming a single
  time-sorted pass over chunked data per Newton-Raphson iteration, with O(p^2)
  working memory independent of the number of observations.
